1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:41,159
(What did you do?)

4
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,400
(Now,)

5
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,680
(your face,)

6
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,200
(your clothes,)

7
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:49,400
(and your identity...)

8
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,079
(Your everything)

9
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,920
(belongs to me now.)

10
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,400
(What's happening?)

11
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:56,640
(What's happening?)

12
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,239
(I'll truly miss this face.)

13
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,120
(What are you trying to do?)

14
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,039
(I'm going to make you)

15
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,319
(die in my place.)

16
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,520
(So that's it.)

17
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:19,840
(To make you believe completely,)

18
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:22,400
(I transferred the camellia mark)

19
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,319
(onto Rong Zhaohua.)

20
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,080
(So you would sense my death.)

21
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,560
(Sister.)

22
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,879
(That day in the woods,)

23
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,439
(Feng Ye did cut my skin.)

24
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,560
(After returning to the palace,)

25
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,479
(I knew he would bring the Emperor)

26
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,520
(to question me.)

27
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:47,400
(So I used the Divine Power)

28
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:49,159
(to transfer the wound)

29
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,560
(silently)

30
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,400
(to a maid beside me.)

31
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,400
(That way,)

32
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,599
(even if he came with his men,)

33
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:58,360
(he would find nothing.)

34
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,639
(And when I imprisoned you
in the Mirror Prison)

35
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:03,479
(and made you endure all that pain,)

36
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,000
(it was to help you)

37
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,000
(break through
the Divine Power's limits.)

38
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,520
(Only then)

39
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,520
(could you truly stand by my side.)

40
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,719
(So all along,)

41
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:23,039
(Rong Zhaohua was you?)

42
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:25,560
(I used the Divine Power
to control Rong Xiu,)

43
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,479
(but he broke free.)

44
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,280
(Was that also your doing?)

45
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,240
(Brother.)

46
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,120
(No.)

47
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,879
(Brother.)

48
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,080
(No.)

49
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,199
(Don't...)

50
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,360
(Brother.)

51
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,439
(I've already sent for His Majesty.)

52
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:40,879
(Guess)

53
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:42,680
(when he sees this,)

54
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,879
(how will he deal with you?)

55
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,039
(My Divine Power,)

56
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:57,080
(why isn't it working?)

57
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,319
(Brother.)

58
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,280
(Zhaohua.)

59
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,599
(I...)

60
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,319
(Zhaohua.)

61
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:27,319
(Zhaohua.)

62
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,000
(How do you have the Divine Power too?)

63
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,639
(Who are you?)

64
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:42,120
(I was going to keep you around.)

65
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,000
(But since this is the case,)

66
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,399
(go join your sister.)

67
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:18,560
(His Majesty arrives!)

68
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,199
(So all of this)

69
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:44,959
(was part of your plan.)

70
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,839
(Since I'm already here,)

71
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,000
(why didn't you)

72
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,879
(reveal yourself to me sooner?)

73
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,480
(To temper you, of course.)

74
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,759
(You grew up in a cage.)

75
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:59,040
(You rarely had the chance
to train the Divine Power.)

76
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:01,360
(And the best way to strengthen it)

77
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,839
(is through hatred.)

78
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,120
(Before this, I thought)

79
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,319
(that if I could control Zhu Yunqi,)

80
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,959
(I could control the realm.)

81
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,560
(But that's not true.)

82
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,959
(He rose from a forsaken prince)

83
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,319
(to the supreme ruler.)

84
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:15,720
(His will is too strong.)

85
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,279
(I could barely control him.)

86
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,399
(If I forced it,)

87
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,800
(it would backfire.)

88
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,199
(I also knew)

89
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,319
(that even if I killed him,)

90
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:26,160
(the realm wouldn't belong to me.)

91
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,319
(Unless I could bear him a prince.)

92
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,439
(Of course,)

93
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,639
(beyond that,)

94
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:33,959
(I needed to find someone else)

95
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,279
(to counter them,)

96
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,439
(to divide)

97
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:38,120
(and dismantle them.)

98
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,079
(That person)

99
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,839
(was Feng Ye.)

100
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,759
(I arranged for Feng Ye
to escort you to the palace,)

101
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,480
(so you could get close to him.)

102
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,279
(He carried a blood debt,)

103
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,879
(so he would surely work with you.)

104
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,160
(Although he once helped)

105
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,920
(Zhu Yunqi seize the throne,)

106
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:55,199
(there was already tension
between them.)

107
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,319
(With a little push,)

108
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:58,079
(they would turn against each other.)

109
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:59,319
(If Feng Ye took the throne,)

110
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,399
(he could kill Zhu Yunqi for me,)

111
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:04,040
(and I would reap the rewards.)

112
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,959
(I'm afraid)

113
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:07,839
(I have to disappoint you, sister.)

114
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:09,199
(Feng Ye and I)

115
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:12,000
(are no longer together.)

116
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,839
(It doesn't matter.)

117
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,480
(He's already served his purpose.)

118
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,120
(Besides,)

119
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:26,040
(everything is still
going according to plan.)

120
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,959
(But when it comes to Feng Ye,)

121
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:29,399
(I miscalculated.)

122
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,199
(Why?)

123
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:32,439
(You must be wondering)

124
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,639
(why Feng Ye suddenly
broke his promise.)

125
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:38,040
(Zhu Yunqi met him in private
and told him)

126
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:39,959
(about his true lineage,)

127
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,959
(that he was the child born
after the late Emperor)

128
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,360
(violated Minister Ruan's wife.)

129
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:47,959
(I always found it strange.)

130
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,920
(Though Feng Ye was driven by revenge,)

131
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,639
(as the son of Minister Ruan,)

132
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,720
(his fate felt far too powerful.)

133
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,079
(It seems)

134
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:57,519
(he was the one destined
to claim the throne.)

135
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,480
(He actually...)

136
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,160
(That weak man)

137
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,319
(lets emotions rule him.)

138
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,639
(He'll never amount to anything.)

139
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,720
(But luckily,)

140
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,560
(I have a full plan now.)

141
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,480
(Consort Rong.)

142
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,480
(His Majesty is here.)

143
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,759
(Don't kill me.)

144
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,759
(Over these past days,)

145
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,279
(Zhu Yunqi's feelings for me
have grown deeper.)

146
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,120
(Soon,)

147
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,919
(he will come to save me.)

148
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,480
(Then,)

149
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:50,480
(you can pretend your revenge failed)

150
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,440
(and return to Feng Ye.)

151
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,480
(Feng Ye has lost his will to fight.)

152
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,919
(Seeing you defeated)

153
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,960
(and hopeless,)

154
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,240
(he will want to take you away.)

155
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,759
(You)

156
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:03,440
(should agree to it.)

157
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:08,639
(Then we'll collude
with Lord of Zhenbei)

158
00:09:08,639 --> 00:09:09,919
(and have him attack the city.)

159
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:12,200
(Use Lord of Zhenbei's hand)

160
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:14,159
(to eliminate Zhu Yunqi.)

161
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,519
(And I)

162
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,759
(will personally eliminate
Lord of Zhenbei)

163
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,399
(and his rebel forces.)

164
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,080
(With Zhu Yunqi gone,)

165
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,679
(no one will stand in my way.)

166
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,720
(Besides,)

167
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,919
(I've borne His Majesty a son.)

168
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,960
(A mother's status rises with her child.)

169
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,840
(When that time comes,)

170
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:35,279
(I will be above)

171
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,919
(the Emperor.)

172
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:39,559
(I will be the sole ruler of Kun.)

173
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,559
Are you satisfied with my plan,

174
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:45,720
Your Majesty?

175
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:48,120
Once you are dead,

176
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,720
I and your son

177
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,600
will be the next rulers.

178
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,639
And true power

179
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:58,159
will rest in my hands.

180
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,200
Zhaohua.

181
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:00,879
No.

182
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:01,639
Yusang.

183
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:04,080
Why did you do this to me?

184
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,279
Why?

185
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,840
Your power-hungry kind forced me.

186
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:12,440
Our Zhao Tribe sits on the border.

187
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,320
We've suffered from war for years.

188
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,440
Our people barely survive.

189
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,960
Outsiders often

190
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,240
seize our women

191
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,000
as playthings,

192
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,159
only to discard them.

193
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,799
Back then, I thought,

194
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:24,519
why should men always be above,

195
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,679
and women below?

196
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,639
I, Jiang Yusang,

197
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,039
will change everything.

198
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:34,720
Yusang.

199
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,120
If you're willing,

200
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,080
this realm,

201
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:38,559
I will share with you.

202
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,480
You'd share it with me?

203
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,240
Why should it be up to you?

204
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:51,039
I will never allow
a ruler as filthy as you

205
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:53,039
to stand above me.

206
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,320
I've already won.

207
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,080
Once you're dead,

208
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:02,000
power will be mine.

209
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,039
Rong Zhaohua.

210
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,440
Stop!

211
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,720
She is Yusang.

212
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,159
A clever escape.

213
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,440
You came after all.

214
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,639
I know the Jiang Yukui I met

215
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:48,799
would never give up on revenge.

216
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,320
How I wish

217
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,879
you truly wanted to leave with me.

218
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:55,320
But I realized, from start to finish,

219
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,000
it was only

220
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,559
me fooling myself.

221
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:04,720
Kui, don't listen to him.

222
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,799
The day you chose Zhu Yunqi,

223
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:10,679
you had already abandoned Kui.

224
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:12,000
If you truly loved her,

225
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,440
wouldn't you have avenged her?

226
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,879
You weren't dead at all.

227
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,159
What was there to avenge?

228
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,879
What about the Zhao Tribe's

229
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:19,039
quest for restoration?

230
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:23,240
You say I abandoned Yukui
for brotherhood.

231
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:27,639
But did you ever truly care for her?

232
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:30,360
She is my own sister.

233
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:32,840
Of course I care for her.

234
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,960
Care?

235
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,440
Your own sister?

236
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,559
You never treated her

237
00:12:36,559 --> 00:12:37,679
as a sister.

238
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:39,919
You used her as your tool.

239
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,279
When I learned that Yukui

240
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:49,000
grew up in a cage,

241
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,080
I looked into it.

242
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,399
That's right.

243
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,840
Your Zhao Tribe does believe

244
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,440
that twin girls bring misfortune.

245
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,240
But you,

246
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,399
as the most revered Holy Maiden,

247
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,919
could have freed Yukui

248
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:05,080
with just one word.

249
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,159
But you didn't.

250
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:08,159
(I came back to you, didn't I,)

251
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:08,799
(Kui?)

252
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,279
(Listen to me.)

253
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,600
(Stay here in this cage.)

254
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:15,039
(One day,)

255
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,799
(I will take you out.)

256
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,320
You chose to cage her,

257
00:13:24,559 --> 00:13:25,440
isolate her,

258
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,200
because only then

259
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,000
would her world have only you,

260
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,759
and she would obey you

261
00:13:30,759 --> 00:13:32,039
and serve your purposes.

262
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:32,679
She would become

263
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:34,559
the stepping stone to your power!

264
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:35,799
You're lying!

265
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:39,120
Everything I did was for Kui,

266
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:41,279
to free her from imperial oppression.

267
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:43,240
Some sacrifices are necessary!

268
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,879
Rising to power by sacrificing others.

269
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:46,639
How are you any different from them?

270
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:38,140
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

271
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:40,060
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

272
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:43,380
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

273
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:47,500
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

274
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:52,180
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

275
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:53,700
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

276
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:57,460
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

277
00:14:57,460 --> 00:15:01,460
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

278
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:05,780
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

279
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:09,340
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

280
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:11,660
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

281
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:15,860
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

282
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,940
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

283
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:19,460
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

284
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:22,660
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

285
00:15:23,060 --> 00:15:24,980
♪In dreams, it's you♪

286
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:26,380
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

287
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:29,700
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

288
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:33,100
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

289
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:36,660
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

290
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:39,900
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

291
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:43,340
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
